    <exercise>
      <title>Parameter Value Problem</title>
      <statement>
        <p>For what values of <m>k</m> does the equation <m>9^{x^2}=27^{x+k}</m> have no real solution?</p>
      </statement>
      <hint>
        <p><m>2x^2-3x-3k=0</m></p>
      </hint>
      <answer>
        <p>The equation has no real solution when <m>k\lt -\frac{3}{8}</m>.</p>
      </answer>
    </exercise>
    
